<i>noun</i>: 치욕감 [치욕깜], 치욕 [치욕], 욕 [욕], 수치심 [수치심], 수치감 [수치감], 수치 [수치], 수모 [수모], 봉변 [봉변], 능욕 [능욕], 굴욕적 [구룍쩍], 굴욕감 [구룍깜], 굴욕 [구룍], 개망신 [개ː망신] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>치욕감 [치욕깜]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>욕되고 창피스러운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being dishonored and ashamed.</dd><br>
<dt>치욕 [치욕]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>욕되고 창피스러움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being dishonored and ashamed.</dd><br>
<dt>욕 [욕]</dt><br>
<dd>1. foul language; abusive language</dd><br>
<dd>남을 무시하거나 비난하는 상스러운 말.</dd><br>
<dd>Vulgar words used to ignore or criticize someone.</dd><br>
<dd>2. reproach; rebuke</dd><br>
<dd>잘못을 해서 듣는 꾸지람.</dd><br>
<dd>A scolding that one gets when one makes a mistake.</dd><br>
<dd>3. shame; humiliation</dd><br>
<dd>부끄럽고 치욕스러운 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Something disgraceful and dishonorable.</dd><br>
<dd>4. labor; pains</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 수고.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) Trouble.</dd><br>
<dt>수치심 [수치심]</dt><br>
<dd>shame; humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>매우 창피하고 부끄러운 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being extremely shameful and embarrassed.</dd><br>
<dt>수치감 [수치감]</dt><br>
<dd>shame; humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>매우 창피하고 부끄러운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being extremely shameful and embarrassed.</dd><br>
<dt>수치 [수치]</dt><br>
<dd>shame; humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>매우 창피하고 부끄러움. 또는 그런 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being extremely shameful and embarrassed, or such an event.</dd><br>
<dt>수모 [수모]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation; indignity</dd><br>
<dd>모욕을 당함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being humiliated.</dd><br>
<dt>봉변 [봉변]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation; unexpected incident</dd><br>
<dd>뜻밖의 사고나 망신스러운 일을 당함. 또는 그 사고나 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The experience of an unexpected or humiliating incident; such an incident or matter.</dd><br>
<dt>능욕 [능욕]</dt><br>
<dd>1. insult; humiliation</dd><br>
<dd>남을 하찮게 여겨 욕되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An insult at another person by belittling him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rape; assault</dd><br>
<dd>여자를 강간하여 욕되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An insult at a female by raping her.</dd><br>
<dt>굴욕적 [구룍쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 업신여김을 받아 창피를 당하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being humiliated by another's contempt for you.</dd><br>
<dt>굴욕감 [구룍깜]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 업신여김을 당해 창피하고 괴로운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>An embarrassing and painful feeling due to another's contempt for you.</dd><br>
<dt>굴욕 [구룍]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 업신여김을 당해 창피함.</dd><br>
<dd>Embarrassment from another's contempt.</dd><br>
<dt>개망신 [개ː망신]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 아주 심한 망신.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) Very severe embarrassment.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>